Toshiba Chemical opens Singapore plant . Japan ' s Toshiba Chemical Corp opened a Singapore $ 57 million chemical plant here on Thursday , a company statement said . The plant , which produces epoxy moulding compounds , insulating varnishes and casting resins used in electronics , started operations in March . Toshiba has 16 companies in Singapore and expects sales in 1997 of Singapore $ 20 million , rising to $ 60 million by 2000 , the statement said . - - Singapore Newsroom ( 65 8703081 ) 
